Re @MultichainOrg  果然出事了， 就知道不靠谱，大半年前就不推荐用了。 之前提供bug录屏报告了，他们开发者一顿调试确认bug，就是不修，拖着奖金不发装无视。  一周后被黑了几千万，才跑去修。

It’s pretty funny how credit card data is slowing dramatically in real time and we still have long threads about how inflation is “entrenched” lol

Bob Elliott: The US economy has shifted from a supply-driven inflation shock to an entrenched inflation dynamic.
Today's PCE report highlights how elevated income growth maintains elevated nominal spending which keeps inflation well above the Fed's mandate.
Core PCE inflation still at 5%: https://t.co/gZcWLgI7SR
